      <hedline>
        <hl1>The Real Thing</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Katherine Roberts letter praises Jonathan Reynolds's August 27 Food column on heirloom tomatoes (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Jonathan Reynolds's article on heirloom tomatoes (Food, Aug. 27) was clever and informative and managed to plug organic farming and thumb its nose at Monsanto at the same time. I had just polished off a wonderful salad Caprese of organic heirlooms, fresh basil and fresh mozzarella before reading it. It was like finding the perfect after-dinner drink.</p>
        <p>Katherine Roberts  San Francisco</p>
      </block>
